headline: Hospital shares slide as latest Senate version seen ’worse’ than anticipated
summary: Investing.com -- Shares of some hospital stocks fell premarket on Monday after BofA analysts warned the latest version of the Senate’s Reconciliation Bill appears “more negative for hospitals” than previously expected.
